        <p>
            <span style="font-size: 18px"><span style="color: #ff8c00">Features</span></span></p>
        <ul style="line-height:25px">
            <li>
                Signatures are stored in High definition .svg images in the attachment of the object and also chatter feed record is also created with image preview of the signature </li>
            <li>
                Has customisable disclaimer stored in custom labels and supports upto 8K characters</li>
            <li>
                Theme,look and feel is set to Salesforce1 styles. Styles can be further configured based on business needs</li>
            <li>
                Additional validations can be added before capturing the signature </li>
            <li>
